  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "把无穷多个幂函数项加在一起，就得到了一个幂级数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "它的形式是常数项，加一次项，加二次项，一直加下去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "神奇的是，这样一串无穷相加，往往能精确等于一个我们熟悉的函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "partial-1",
      "filename": "partial-partial-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/partial-partial-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "我们没法真的加无穷项，于是只取前面有限的几项，叫做部分和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "partial-2",
      "filename": "partial-partial-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/partial-partial-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "看这条黄色曲线，它就是部分和画出来的图像。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "partial-3",
      "filename": "partial-partial-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/partial-partial-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "项数越多，黄色曲线就越贴近蓝色的精确函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "radius",
      "line_id": "radius-1",
      "filename": "radius-radius-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/radius-radius-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "但逼近并不是处处都成立，这里有一条无形的边界。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "radius",
      "line_id": "radius-2",
      "filename": "radius-radius-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/radius-radius-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "这条边界到原点的距离，就叫收敛半径，用红色虚线标出。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "radius",
      "line_id": "radius-3",
      "filename": "radius-radius-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/radius-radius-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "在边界以内，级数收敛；越过边界，无论加多少项都会发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "why",
      "line_id": "why-1",
      "filename": "why-why-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/why-why-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "几何级数是最简单的例子，收敛半径正好等于一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "why",
      "line_id": "why-2",
      "filename": "why-why-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/why-why-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "而指数级数的收敛半径是无穷大，它在整条数轴上都收敛。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "试着增加项数，看黄色曲线在边界以内一点点压到蓝线上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "再切换不同的级数，比较它们收敛半径的差别。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "幂级数用无穷项相加逼近函数，部分和项数越多越准。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "收敛半径划定了逼近成立的范围，内收敛而外发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-series",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-series/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.51,
      "size": 24192,
      "text": "有限的项，无穷的逼近，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
